      <p class="intertitre"><a href="../corpus/show_text.php?id=crdo-NEP_RAUT69_SOUND&idref=crdo-NEP_RAUT69"><img src="../../images/icones/Txt_Inter_parchemin.jpg" alt="a" width="20" height="20" border="0">Rani Raut</a><br>
